{"tid":816214,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解啲人話識親都係player？","createTime":"2018-09-12T14:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T15:18:15.000Z","uid":7805,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc849dfbe348735c47e9205d7f3df729786fb7c2","tid":816214,"uid":7805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T14:59:33.000Z","msg":"你有無諗過<br />\n其實係啲player識得點樣令人<br />\n集中焦點落自己到<br />\n點解一大班frd入面<br />\n你淨係留意到佢？<br />\n因為佢Yo？因為佢搞笑？<br />\n係因為佢一開頭對個個都咁好<br />\n你係佢其中一個<br />\n咁點解會無視左其他人<br />\n因為佢地唔急於表現自己<br />\n慢慢從旁觀察同溝通<br />\n當然都有鐘意突出自己而唔係player嘅人<br />\n反之亦然<br />\n不過，想食快餐唔通仲慢慢等咩<br />\n好似點解永遠覺得生活上<br />\n唔開心嘅事多過開心嘅事<br />\n因為唔開心感受深刻過開心<br />\n而快樂總是一瞬間<br />\n你有咁嘅感受嘅話<br />\n請你好好帶眼識人<br />\n最後，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Player仆街含撚死</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e998a9a14e47705a9591d5b29698806994cefa","tid":816214,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"894d94c8ebdd3a8470317613774bb557a35600bf","tid":816214,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"ready player one"},{"pid":"9219d9c06aae6b5c66970c3e73f5a1db906fbf4e","tid":816214,"uid":30751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"因為player都係靚仔/女"},{"pid":"7105d1ce29b7ca7897bda14d32291c627e6eea0a","tid":816214,"uid":7805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e998a9a14e47705a9591d5b29698806994cefa","tid":816214,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"pmed<br />\n約屌你條腸ok？"},{"pid":"61663cf938cfc4e751df35d46ba93b2ec58191d4","tid":816214,"uid":7805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9219d9c06aae6b5c66970c3e73f5a1db906fbf4e","tid":816214,"uid":30751,